📌 Overview

This is a console-based Stock Management System developed in C++ as an Introduction to Computing (ITC) course project.

The project helps users manage product inventory by allowing them to add, view, search, edit, and sell products while monitoring low stock levels.

✨ Features

➕ Add new products
📋 View all products
🔍 Search products by ID
💰 Sell products
⚠️ Low stock alert
✏️ Edit product details
🆔 Automatic Product ID generation
✅ Input validation for price and quantity

